It even includes several paint-on actions for more fine-tuned editing! Including one for adding light, and one for painting the leaves or greenery of your photos!

Also included in this set is a 'Play-All' action which runs every action in the set and turns the visibility off. This allows you to more quickly and easily see what each action does by simply scrolling through your layers panel and turning the visibility on and off for each one. This way you don't have to select and play every action individually, you can get a quicker grasp of the way they look and acquaint yourself with them- allowing yourself to achieve quicker processing later!
